title: Surbhi Chandna Is Missing Navina Bole; Also Read What Ishqbaaz Team Gifted Navina & Jeet!
text:
¬ª Surbhi Chandna Is Missing Navina Bole; Also Read What Ishqbaaz Team Gifted Navina & Jeet! Surbhi Chandna Is Missing Navina Bole; Also Read What Ishqbaaz Team Gifted Navina & Jeet! Ishqbaaz actress Navina Bole recently got married and is on a holiday. Her co-actress Surbhi Chandna is already missing her. Do you know what Surbhi and team gifted Navina on her wedding? Updated:   17:47   
Actress Surbhi Chandna , who plays the role of Anika in Star Plus' popular show Ishqbaaz , is missing Navina Bole (Tia) big time! On the show, Tia and Ankita are enemies (sautan), but off-screen they bond really well. They spend a lot of time cracking jokes! Well, we are not the ones saying it! Surbhi's post says it all. Read on.... Surbhi Chandna Is Missing Navina Bole 
Surbhi shared a picture of Navina and wrote, "Stunner this is when i secretly captured you. Hey i am missing doing scenes with you Tia baby and cracking up for no reason." Surbhi & Navina 
"Your valuable tips ,Our chicken (non vegetarian) jokes i miss the most. Pls make the most of this new phase you are entering into.Get done with everything and see us on set very soon." Surbhi Asks Navina To Enjoy Vacation On Her Behalf! 
"cant wait to have you backüòöoh since i cant get a vacation pls have fun on my behalf on your SHEHADCHAAND. Much love to YOU and JEET." Ishqbaaz Team At Navina-Jeet Wedding 
Apparently, Ishqbaaz team had made a Whatsapp group in which they had a discussion regarding Navina's wedding preparations - what to wear and what to gift, etc! Navina Was Waiting For This Day! 
Surbhi spoke to media and said that Navina didn't have time for preparation, yet she had managed to make it a grand event. She added that Navina was waiting for this day. What Ishqbaaz Team Gifted Navina-Jeet! 
Surbhi wished Navina, a happy married life and also revealed the gift! Apparently, the Ishqbaaz team gifted Navina with a precious gift - a Bose Music system. Nakuul had also wished Navina and said that they will miss her. The actor shared his and Tia's wedding picture and wrote, "Couldn't think of a better wedding present than giving you a dress rehearsal officially on set.""It has been such a joy ride working with you. You have continued to amaze me with your impeccable dress sense, panache, warmth & hard to copy Bandra accent. ;-) Thank you for also giving me the worst on screen couple acronym - 'Shitia' although it's hard to imagine anybody else pulling off that with such aplomb.""You shall be missed on set but go right ahead and have a banging honeymoon. Photos & videos awaited with much eagerness. :-) And just a reminder - 4 days to go! ‚ù§ @navina_005."Navina and Karan Jeet wedding was a grand event. The reception was no less than an 'Ishqbaaz affair' as Navina's co-stars graced the event. The team had a gala time during Navina and Jeet's reception party. We had also reported that the team had a blast at the after party, as the entire team went out for dinner. Apart from Ishqbaaz team, Navina and Jeet's reception was also attended by Arjun Bijlani, his wife Neha Swami, Navina's close friends Niti Taylor and Gia Manek.
(Images Source: Instagram)
